// Pixel-art icons v4 (matched to Trym's reference pack): soft dark outlines
// (dark plum, not pure black — visible on dark buttons), bright modern
// colours, internal dimensional shading with dithering, and FULL-BLEED
// square-ish tiles — every glyph fills its box (the letterboxing was why v3
// icons looked small next to the palette). ASCII maps on a 10-unit grid →
// crispEdges SVG rects. Letter M = currentColor for mono UI glyphs.
// Iterate art in the scratchpad Pillow preview (white/banana/black swatches)
// before touching this file.
